Distribution . Found in Chile from northern Coquimbo Province to northern Los Lagos Province and in the western part of Neuquén Province, Argentina from from late October to mid March at nearly sea level to 2300m (
Fig. 23
).

Etymology. Named for French herpetologist Jean Théodore Cocteau (
1798–1838
).
